@vars d=SKIP_METHODS
findJSFiles(dir,rootDir=)→parseGitignore,readdirSync,join,relative,statSync,stat.isDirectory|recursively find JS files applying filter rules
findJSDocBefore(comments,targetLine)|null|null|null|find JSDoc block immediately preceding a line
extractComments(code)→regex.exec,code.slice,comments.push|extract all JSDoc blocks and their end lines
checkMissing(jsdoc,level)→missing.push,jsdoc.includes|check if JSDoc is missing required tags for strictness level
export checkUndocumentedFile(code,filePath,level)→parse,extractComments,findJSDocBefore,results.push,methodName.startsWith,SKIP_METHODS.includes|analyze single file for undocumented classes, functions, methods
export getUndocumented(dir,level=)→resolve,findJSFiles,readFileSync,relative,checkUndocumentedFile,results.push|scan directory for all undocumented items
export getUndocumentedSummary(dir,level=)→getUndocumented,items.filter,items.slice|scan directory and return aggregated undocumented summary
PATTERNS: AST traversal|regex JSDoc extraction
EDGE_CASES: skips lifecycle methods|skips private prefixed methods